<section class="fg-search-hero">
  <div class="fg-search-shell">
    <div class="fg-search-left">
      <p class="fg-eyebrow">Immobiliengesuch & Vormerkung</p>
      <h1>Passende Immobilien zuerst erhalten.</h1>
      <p class="fg-lead">
        Hinterlegen Sie Ihre Suchkriterien. Wir merken Sie für passende Angebote vor und informieren Sie persönlich, sobald eine Immobilie zu Ihren Wünschen passt.
      </p>
      <div class="fg-benefits">
        <div><i class="fas fa-check"></i><span>Persönliche Vorprüfung Ihrer Angaben</span></div>
        <div><i class="fas fa-check"></i><span>Vormerkung für passende Immobilienangebote</span></div>
        <div><i class="fas fa-check"></i><span>Auf Wunsch auch diskrete Off-Market-Hinweise</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fg-search-card">
      <div class="fg-progress-wrap">
        <span id="fg-step-label">Schritt 1 von 4</span>
        <div class="fg-progress"><div id="fg-progress-bar"></div></div>
      </div>

      <form id="fg-search-profile-form" novalidate>
        <div class="fg-status fg-success" hidden>
          Vielen Dank. Ihr Gesuch wurde erfolgreich übermittelt. Wir melden uns, sobald ein passendes Angebot vorliegt.
        </div>
        <div class="fg-status fg-error" hidden>
          Die Übermittlung war nicht erfolgreich. Bitte prüfen Sie Ihre Angaben oder versuchen Sie es später erneut.
        </div>

        <div class="fg-step is-active" data-step="1">
          <p class="fg-mini">Ihre Suche</p>
          <h2>Wonach suchen Sie?</h2>
          <div class="fg-choice-grid two">
            <label class="fg-choice"><input type="radio" name="marketing_type" value="BUY" checked><span><i class="fas fa-key"></i>Kaufen</span></label>
            <label class="fg-choice"><input type="radio" name="marketing_type" value="RENT"><span><i class="fas fa-door-open"></i>Mieten</span></label>
          </div>
          <h3>Welche Objektart passt?</h3>
          <div class="fg-choice-grid">
            <label class="fg-choice"><input type="radio" name="property_type" value="Wohnung" checked><span><i class="fas fa-building"></i>Wohnung</span></label>
            <label class="fg-choice"><input type="radio" name="property_type" value="Haus"><span><i class="fas fa-house"></i>Haus</span></label>
            <label class="fg-choice"><input type="radio" name="property_type" value="Mehrfamilienhaus"><span><i class="fas fa-city"></i>Mehrfamilienhaus</span></label>
            <label class="fg-choice"><input type="radio" name="property_type" value="Grundstück"><span><i class="fas fa-map"></i>Grundstück</span></label>
            <label class="fg-choice"><input type="radio" name="property_type" value="Gewerbe"><span><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i>Gewerbe</span></label>
            <label class="fg-choice"><input type="radio" name="property_type" value="Kapitalanlage"><span><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>Kapitalanlage</span></label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fg-step" data-step="2">
          <p class="fg-mini">Suchgebiet & Rahmen</p>
          <h2>Wo und in welchem Rahmen?</h2>
          <div class="fg-field">
            <label>Suchgebiet *</label>
            <input class="fg-input google-address" name="location" required placeholder="z. B. Berlin, Potsdam, Charlottenburg">
          </div>
          <div class="fg-form-grid three">
            <div class="fg-field"><label>Budget / Preis bis</label><input class="fg-input js-money" name="budget" inputmode="numeric" placeholder="z. B. 750.000 €"></div>
            <div class="fg-field"><label>Zimmer ab</label><input class="fg-input js-number" name="rooms" inputmode="decimal" placeholder="z. B. 3"></div>
            <div class="fg-field"><label>Fläche ab m²</label><input class="fg-input js-number" name="living_space" inputmode="numeric" placeholder="z. B. 80"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fg-form-grid three">
            <div class="fg-field"><label>Schlafzimmer ab</label><input class="fg-input js-number" name="bedrooms" inputmode="decimal" placeholder="optional"></div>
            <div class="fg-field"><label>Badezimmer ab</label><input class="fg-input js-number" name="bathrooms" inputmode="decimal" placeholder="optional"></div>
            <div class="fg-field"><label>Grundstück ab m²</label><input class="fg-input js-number" name="plot_area" inputmode="numeric" placeholder="optional"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fg-step" data-step="3">
          <p class="fg-mini">Ausstattung & Wünsche</p>
          <h2>Was ist Ihnen wichtig?</h2>
          <div class="fg-toggle-grid">
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="features" value="Balkon/Terrasse"><span>Balkon/Terrasse</span></label>
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="features" value="Garten"><span>Garten</span></label>
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="features" value="Aufzug"><span>Aufzug</span></label>
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="features" value="Keller"><span>Keller</span></label>
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="features" value="Stellplatz"><span>Stellplatz</span></label>
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="features" value="Barrierefrei"><span>Barrierefrei</span></label>
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="features" value="Einbauküche"><span>Einbauküche</span></label>
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="features" value="Off-Market interessant"><span>Off-Market interessant</span></label>
          </div>
          <div class="fg-field mt-4">
            <label>Weitere Wünsche</label>
            <textarea class="fg-input" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="z. B. Lage, Zustand, Rendite, Finanzierung, zeitlicher Rahmen"></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fg-step" data-step="4">
          <p class="fg-mini">Kontakt</p>
          <h2>Wie dürfen wir Sie erreichen?</h2>
          <div class="fg-form-grid two">
            <div class="fg-field"><label>Vorname</label><input class="fg-input" name="first_name" placeholder="Vorname"></div>
            <div class="fg-field"><label>Nachname</label><input class="fg-input" name="last_name" placeholder="Nachname"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="fg-form-grid two">
            <div class="fg-field"><label>E-Mail-Adresse *</label><input class="fg-input" name="email" type="email" required placeholder="name@beispiel.de"></div>
            <div class="fg-field"><label>Telefonnummer</label><input class="fg-input" name="phone" type="tel" placeholder="optional"></div>
          </div>
          <label class="fg-consent">
            <input type="checkbox" name="privacy_consent" value="true" required>
            <span>Ich möchte passende Immobilienangebote sowie den Newsletter erhalten und habe die <a href="/datenschutz.html" target="_blank">Datenschutzerklärung</a> gelesen. *</span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <div class="fg-actions">
          <button type="button" class="fg-back" id="fg-back" disabled>Zurück</button>
          <button type="button" class="fg-next" id="fg-next">Weiter</button>
          <button type="submit" class="fg-next" id="fg-submit" hidden>Gesuch übermitteln</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
